text: East Kalimantan (Indonesian: Kalimantan Timur) is a province in the island of Borneo. The Indonesian future capital, Nusantara, will be in Sepaku, Penajam Paser Utara Regency. The capital is in Samarinda. The economy of Balikpapan eight times are more "maju" than the capital province.
title: East Kalimantan
